eft class=m><span class=title> Re: Questions about a Fear CR</span><hr size=1> Zone in with 3 groups.  Clerics, Wizzies/mages/druids, 3 enchanters, and one crazy bard.  Bard runs and brings back 10-15 mobs at a time and chain stun while all casters AoE.  We cleared Fear in 40 minutes minus the Demis that night. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Then again, we've had 3hr breaks in fear due to wipeouts.  All I know is Fear can be a real pain to break and I don't particularly care for the zone.  Only reason people go there is for epic pieces IMHO.  The usual method is to run straight to the wall and try to survive all the adds.  We normally CR there but the corner is the best spot.<br>
